* Dinobot smiled to himself as he watched Scourge's body fumble around for 
his head, why was it so funny when Predacon's were defeated?
He looked around and saw Scourge's head, he walked over to it and kicked it 
as hard as he could...sending it a few hundred metres in the distance.
Dinobot then looked at the Suukie and growled as he saw him shoot at 
Tavatron, he targeted his chest and shot at the pathetic transformer. Nobot 
betrayed him and got away with it!!
Just then Dinobot glanced towards the Ark and saw Rampage enter into the 
ship, he snarled and glanced back at Tavatron. She was continuing to fight 
BrightBlade and he knew that she was to busy to bother with the invading 
enemies right now...so it was up to him.
Dinobot wiped the mech fluid from his face and walked towards the Ark, on 
his way by he retrieved his rifle and reloaded it. It just might come in 
handy.*
